{"tid":462071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：社民連投年宵　靠777嚇退對手 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-11-08T08:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6abfcb944f651a6bd9e6dabfe163fdeb5de0a2","tid":462071,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171108/20207706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F20207706&d=2UPFK%2FPzvf41uQ%2F%2F0eDloXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6209f54a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F20207706&h=0a353dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171108/20207706</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：社民連投年宵　靠777嚇退對手 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171108/large/a1204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171108%2Flarge%2Fa1204a.gif&h=5acf482f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳文遠<br />\n<br />\n話咁快就嚟年尾，又係競投年宵市場攤位嘅日子喇！今年各大政黨一如以往競投維園嘅年宵攤位，點知一向投開6號攤位嘅社民連竟然遇到阿姐疑似托價，主席吳文遠惟有用「777」呢個今年特首選舉後，因林鄭而被賦予新意思嘅數字，嚇走競爭者，仲贏得全場掌聲㖭。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠話今年年宵攤位嘅成交價普遍較低，原本以為用萬零蚊就投到攤位，但遇到阿姐疑似托價，當叫價去到兩萬幾時，佢一度以「2萬9千689」打算嚇走阿姐，點知阿姐唔怕「689」，仲一托就托到3萬。吳文遠最後以3萬零777元投得攤位，大呻成本較預期高！佢話今年年宵除咗會繼續諷刺林鄭小恩小惠嘅施政方針，更會呼籲大家支持政治犯，指社民連有多人面對訴訟，叫大家踴躍捐輸。<br />\n<br />\n至於每年都會競投維園年宵1、2號攤位嘅支聯會，今年就以33,100元投得兩個攤位，比上年慳咗18,500元。據知支聯會年宵檔貨品同劉曉波、劉霞及民主女神像有關。"},{"pid":"281c9e665631501dfcba6b01308a0cda5cd60864","tid":462071,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12d6ee084f140519ea3935595382bad8e633f9a3","tid":462071,"uid":52148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左膠式抗爭我地真係識條鐵咩"},{"pid":"311735371ed9fb6d7d8a3d6cad18d63b7a5e43cd","tid":462071,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T18:58:55.000Z","msg":"錢搵錢你地識咩"},{"pid":"7d8b35979005b03ce67d365f921b3ce4189a5a40","tid":462071,"uid":43085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"熱狗有冇攪年宵"},{"pid":"b01e5e853a45cf13506adde50071954429412865","tid":462071,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"佢地係入續社運方面真係有一手，呢層熱狗要學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}